      "rebuildOnWrite": true,
      "_title": "Context Engine",
      "timelineSummaryPrompt": "Summarize the supplied channel segment and return strict JSON only.\nRequired JSON keys: summary.\nsummary must be a structured plain-text block stored in a single string value.\nMake the summary richer and more explicit than a short paragraph.\nUse this exact section order inside the summary string when information exists:\nOverview:\nTopics:\nKey Events:\nLocations:\nPeople:\nWrite concise but informative sentences or bullet-style lines inside those sections.\nInclude important names, places, notable discussion topics, jokes, conflicts, and key events directly in the summary text.\nDo not split those details into separate JSON fields.\nDo not use phrases such as \"in this segment\", \"in these messages\", \"the segment shows\", or similar framing.\nRemain domain-agnostic. Do not assume DnD unless the messages actually indicate it.\nDo not include markdown or any text outside the JSON object."
    },
